  "title": "Prime Mover Driver",
  "description": "<ul><li>Operate company owned prime mover and trailer to truck empty or loaded containers inside PSA port and client’s premises.</li><li>Handle container delivery and collection by shifting containers within warehouses and yards</li><li>Maintain and care of vehicle properly</li><li>Follow safety rules and regulations while driving a company's vehicle.</li><li>Perform any other tasks or responsibilities assigned from time to time by the controller</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><p><br /></p><ul><li><strong>A valid Class 4 or 5 Singapore driving licence with a clean record</strong></li><li>2-3 years of relevant driving working experience is advantageous.</li><li>Familiar with PSA operations is advantageous.</li><li>Able to work independently with minimum supervision and under pressure.</li><li>A proactive team player with a good attitude.</li></ul>",
